Interface DimensionMatchingIndexFieldHandler<RowType,IndexFieldType extends CommonIndexValue,NativeFieldType>

  • Type Parameters:
    RowType -
    IndexFieldType -
    NativeFieldType -
    All Superinterfaces:
    IndexFieldHandler<RowType,IndexFieldType,NativeFieldType>

    public interface DimensionMatchingIndexFieldHandler<RowType,IndexFieldType extends CommonIndexValue,NativeFieldType>
extends IndexFieldHandler<RowType,IndexFieldType,NativeFieldType>
    This is internally useful for the AbstractDataAdapter to match field handlers with dimensions by field ID. Any fields with the ID returned by getSupportedIndexFieldIds() will use this handler.
